; Verify the full sequence (spindle stop, safe Z, M6/T/H if used) on your control
; before running multi-tool jobs.
; ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
; Work area (mm): 300 x 200 x 100
N10 G21        ; G21=mm / G20=inch — must match controller defaults at power-on
N20 G90              ; absolute distance mode
N30 G17              ; XY plane (typical for G2/G3 arcs)
; Operation: Subs + Line Numbers
; Spindle on (dialect from machine profile — change profile if M3/S/RPM differ)
N40 M3 S10000
N50 G0 X0 Y0 Z10
; --- Subroutine call (4x repeat) ---
N60 M98 P1000 L4
N70 G0 Z10
; Spindle off (dialect snippet — usually M5)
N80 M5
; Retract Z to safe clearance and park (adjust to your machine's preferred home)
N90 G0 Z100 ; safe Z retract — adjust to your actual safe clearance
N100 G0 X0 Y0                     ; park X Y — adjust to your preferred home position
N110 M30

; --- SUBROUTINE DEFINITIONS ---
N120 O1000 (SUBROUTINE 1000)
N130 G0 Z5
N140 G1 Z-1.000 F300
N150 G1 X10 Y0 F800
N160 M99
"
`;

